business.schedule
Class Position

java.lang.Object
  business.BusinessObject
      business.schedule.Position
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Position
extends BusinessObject

This class represents a Position that an employee can work. It is used extensively in Scheduling for auto-generation; it places employees that can work certain positions in those positions that are required for a completely schedule to be generated. (No errors)

Version:
0.2.0
Author:
peon-dev
